BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 702.00 Td (roads were only condition-colored, the DP decision was not obvious.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 683.50 Td (Fix: selected roads are stored as sorted endpoint tuples and rendered in cyan with thicker) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 670.00 Td (lines and a glow layer.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.6 Tf 72 651.50 Td (selected_maintenance.add\(tuple\(sorted\([road['from_id'], road['to_id']]\)\)\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11.2 Tf 58 631.00 Td (4.3 Zoom Was Not Consistent Across Maps) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 613.50 Td (Plotly maps support zoom, but scroll zoom must be explicitly enabled when the toolbar is) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 600.00 Td (hidden. Initially, only the maintenance map had it enabled.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 581.50 Td (Fix: a shared configuration was created and applied to Trip Planner, Emergency Response, MST,) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 568.00 Td (and Maintenance maps.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.6 Tf 72 549.50 Td (PLOTLY_MAP_CONFIG = {'displayModeBar': False, 'scrollZoom': True}) Tj ET
