BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 511.50 Td (edges.csv lists each road once, but most city roads should be traversable both ways. If only) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 498.00 Td (forward edges are stored, routing can fail depending on direction.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 479.50 Td (Fix: the loader stores both forward and reverse adjacency entries. Unique-edge helpers prevent) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 466.00 Td (duplicate display on maps.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11.2 Tf 58 445.50 Td (4.5 Existing Roads Mixed With Potential Roads) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 428.00 Td (The same edge file contains built roads and future candidate roads. Routing must not) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 414.50 Td (accidentally use unbuilt roads, while MST must evaluate them.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 396.00 Td (Fix: Edge exposes is_existing and is_potential based on Cost. Routing defaults to existing) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 382.50 Td (roads, while MST uses potential roads intentionally.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.6 Tf 72 364.00 Td (edge.is_existing  # cost == 0) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.6 Tf 72 350.50 Td (edge.is_potential # cost > 0) Tj ET
BT /F2 11.2 Tf 58 330.00 Td (4.6 DP Budget Required Integer Indexes) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 312.50 Td (The maintenance DP table indexes budgets from 0 to W. Floating repair costs would break safe) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 299.00 Td (indexing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 280.50 Td (Fix: repair_cost is converted to int after calculation, making the DP table deterministic and) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 267.00 Td (index-safe.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11.2 Tf 58 246.50 Td (4.7 Streamlit Reruns Could Reset UI Output) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 229.00 Td (Streamlit reruns the script after widget interactions. Without session state, route results) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 215.50 Td (and selections could disappear.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 197.00 Td (Fix: session state defaults are initialized for route_result, active_page, selected algorithm,) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 183.50 Td (selected time, potential-road toggle, and chaos edges.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11.2 Tf 58 163.00 Td (4.8 Docker Slim Image Needed System Libraries) Tj ET
