BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 132.00 Td (graphical dependencies.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.6 Tf 58 113.50 Td (Fix: the Dockerfile installs build-essential, libglib2.0-0, and libgl1 before installing) Tj ET
